{"TopicId":154202,"ForumId":70,"TopicTitle":"KSP 1.2.2 stuttering every second (now crashing)","CreatedByName":"Voodoo8648","CreatedById":142471,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-30T03:24:45Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Voodoo8648","CreatedById":142471,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-30T03:24:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP seemed\u00A0to have been stuttering every 1/2 second. When I restart my PC and load KSP it worked\u00A0fine for about an hour, but then it started\u00A0\u0022stuttering\u0022 \u00A0or freezing\u00A0for about 1/4 of a second every 1/2 second. It\u0027s worth noting that the frame rate between freezes\u00A0was\u00A0nice and smooth. Now the game is crashing upon loading. Cannot load KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESystem Specs:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCPU: Intel 5930K\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRAM: 32GB DDR4 2666Mhz\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGraphics: 12GB VRAM (GTX Titan X)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://1drv.ms/u/s!AvUWxjgM4SuQhbZ6kZOTDse8oy1kYg\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKSP.log\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://1drv.ms/t/s!AvUWxjgM4SuQhbY4DWrHDN_0tjgcbA\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EOutput_log.txt\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-30T03:34:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe stuttering is a problem with the way unity 5 handles garbage collection. \u00A0More about this problem here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/129562-its-been-6-months-since-i-asked-about-the-stutter/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=2354186\u0026amp;embedComment=2354186\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment#comment-2354186\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs to the crashing and unable to load - If you have the steam version you can verify the game files and see if it starts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Voodoo8648","CreatedById":142471,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-30T04:54:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222904845\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022154202\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221483068876\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe stuttering is a problem with the way unity 5 handles garbage collection. \u00A0More about this problem here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs to the crashing and unable to load - If you have the steam version you can verify the game files and see if it starts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am not running the Steam version. I had recently installed the RealPlume mod, so I removed that mod and I am now\u00A0able to load KSP and the stuttering doesn\u0027t seem to be so bad. The stuttering / freezing only happens about once every 15 seconds now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DeadOnDuna","CreatedById":173703,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-15T13:43:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222904882\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022154202\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221483073641\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142471\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Voodoo8648\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12/30/2016 at 6:54 AM, Voodoo8648 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe stuttering / freezing only happens about once every 15 seconds now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck [1.2.x] MemGraph 1.1.0.3 - with Stutter Reduction\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/139128-12x-memgraph-1103-with-stutter-reduction/\u0026amp;page=1\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}